CollisionHandler    - Handles collision detection and response between entities
ConnectionHandler   - Holds together entities like those making up a ship, and aggregates values like mass and forces
Controller          - Players and AI/NPCs control entities via this subsystem
Graphics            - Draws entities
Physics             - Moves entities
Placer              - Keeps track of entity positions and wraparound
Sound               - Plays sounds and music
Spawner             - Handles entities that can spawn other entities, and values of the spawned entities
Timer               - Keeps track of time for entities that need it